Revision history for DBIO-SQLite

{{$NEXT}}
    - Remove sql_limit_dialect from Storage (uses default apply_limit)
    - Declare DateTime::Format::SQLite as a runtime dependency
    - Add AccessBroker connect smoke coverage for SQLite storage
    - Move remaining driver _ENV_ usage to DBIO::Util helpers
    - Add native Introspect/Diff/DDL/Deploy modules (parallel to the
      DBIO::PostgreSQL set). Replaces the SQL::Translator path for
      schema deployment and diffing:
        . DBIO::SQLite::Introspect (+ Tables, Columns, Indexes,
          ForeignKeys) via sqlite_master and PRAGMAs
        . DBIO::SQLite::DDL generator from Result classes, with
          INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT inline
        . DBIO::SQLite::Diff (+ Table, Column, Index) with columns
          inlined on CREATE TABLE and drop-then-create on index changes
        . DBIO::SQLite::Deploy with install/diff/apply/upgrade using
          an in-memory SQLite as the test-deploy target
    - Add DBIO::SQLite::Result component with sqlite_index declaration
      (consumed by DBIO::SQLite::DDL)
    - Storage now declares dbio_deploy_class so DBIO::Schema->deploy()
      routes through DBIO::SQLite::Deploy instead of SQL::Translator
    - Remove workspace .proverc (tests run against installed dbio core
      via dzil install, no hidden sibling-repo linkage)
    - Add tests: t/30-introspect.t (round-trip with tables, FKs,
      composite FK, partial index, WITHOUT ROWID), t/31-diff.t
      (create/drop/change for tables/columns/indexes plus orchestrator),
      t/32-deploy.t (end-to-end install/diff/apply/upgrade with FK
      relationships via belongs_to)
